@meganrogge only the `navigation` group shows by default and respects `isHiddenByDefault`. Doing this means you cannot toggle visibility of the item:

<img width="347" height="284" alt="Image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/925ede7f-5fd9-4662-b3db-46482f08d551" />

I agree separators are nice, but the point of this was to make it more convenient to use dictation and that requires being able to toggle so it's moved out of the overflow menu.

